2024 EVENTS

The Felton Remembers Parade and Festival 2024!

​Please see the Parade page for registration information for the Memorial Day Parade (May 25, 2024), and for the Covered Bridge Festival. Hope to see you there in downtown Felton, Saturday, May 25, 2024!

You can also visit our Facebook page at:

https://www.facebook.com/FeltonParadeAndFestival
